lead_paragraph: Shortly before sunrise on Tuesday, Morgan Capezzera reclined on the roulette table at the Revel Casino in her bikini and snapped a selfie before the Atlantic City gambling hall shut its doors for good.

headline.main: Last Call at Atlantic City's Revel: a Few Bettors, $5 Bottles, State Cops
